Since I have no way to identify which reminder you’d like to move, I’m unable to perform the reschedule. To change an existing reminder you’ll need to give me at least one of these:

- a phrase from the reminder’s text (I can fuzzy-search with it)  
- the unique reminder ID  
- the original date/time it was set for (so I can look within a range)

Once you have any of those details, let me know and I’ll push it to tomorrow 5 PM.
